review: Dr.Manreet and Dr.Prabhjot are hands down one of the most experienced dentists in town. Literally the best decision ever to choose them for all my dental work. I required braces and Dr.Manreet is looking after my Invisalign treatment and I have to say she is literally the most patient and professional dentist I've ever come across. She's always ready to clear out any doubts that I have. She planned the whole treatment according to my comfort and has so far given the best possible advice for it aswell. The staff is very professional yet sweet. They keep on checking up on you after extractions etc and its the most hygienic clinic. Highly recommended.
reply_text: Thank you for your feedback. Means alot to us.

review: Dr. Manreet is amazing! She’s very passionate about her work, very kind, professional, and friendly. I had braces for years (from a different doctor) and my teeth still didn’t go in, but Dr Manreet gave me confidence that I could have the perfect smile and she could fix it. My previous doctors told me it couldn’t be done, but Dr Manreet’s Invisalign treatment completely fixed my smile and I’ve never felt more confident! Going to her and getting Invisalign has been the best decision I’ve made. Her clinic is clean, very well decorated, the colors and design make you feel warm and comfortable and her staff is very nice. I recommend going here for all your dental needs!
reply_text: Thank you for your feedback. Means alot to us.

review: Dr Manreet Sidhu is a thorough professional. Being somewhat chary of all things medical and having a bad gag reflex does compound my issues when it comes to visiting a dentist. But Dr Sidhu was totally understanding and patient. She dealt with my dental issues as well as anxiety issues so calmly, all the while explaining the procedure to me. To top it all, her clinic is done up really aesthetically. I highly recommend her to all those on a lookout for a good, empathetic *** ************* ******** My search ended here.... yours will too.
reply_text: Thank you for your feedback.

review:
Had a great experience with Dr Manreet Sidhu . Got Invisalign done from her. She did a great job.  My teeth were very
crooked and i had an unpleasent smile .  The Dental experience is very beautiful with great and soothing ambience.

Quick decision making. Answered my questions patiently. Promptly available for follow up. 5 stars to Dr. Sidhu. Thank you.
reply_text: Thank you for your feedback. Means alot to us

review:
One of the gentlest hands, that made my dental sessions so comfortable and put me at ease! Thank you so much Dr Manreet, for your time and patience in accommodating my appointments - you did a commendable job with my teeth. 
All the very best to you and your team!
reply_text: Thank you so much for your feedback. Means alot to us.

review:
Visited her clinic after the first wave of covid. Was amazed to see the level of safety precautions being taken at her clinic. She was recommended to me by a friend. I was quite skeptical at first considering my fear of going to a dentist, but she turned out to be super friendly and I surprisingly had a pain free experience. 


What loved even more was the after service. There were regular calls from the clinic to check up on how I was feeling after the treatment.
reply_text: Thank you for your feedback. Means alot to us.
